  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM pacientes WHERE deleted_at IS NULL) as total_pacientes,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM atendimentos WHERE deleted_at IS NULL) as total_atendimentos,

  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM evolucoes) as evolucoes,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM agendamentos) as agendamentos;
